# .prettierignore
# ==============================================================================
# Arxiu per ignorar fitxers que Prettier NO hauria de reformatejar.
# Util per evitar tocar fitxers generats, configuracio, o binaris.
# ==============================================================================

# === Build & Distribution ===
dist
dist-types
build

# === Dependencies ===
node_modules
packages/*/node_modules

# === Test & Coverage ===
coverage
e2e-test-report
playwright-report
test-results

# === Configuration & Package Files ===
yarn.lock
package-lock.json
pnpm-lock.yaml
.yarn/

# === IDE & Local Configuration ===
.vscode
.idea

# === Generated Files ===
.next
.nuxt
*.tsbuildinfo

# === Cache ===
.eslintcache
.prettierignore.local

# === Documentation (usually pre-formatted) ===
README.md
CHANGELOG.md
